Description_lang: Xal'atath summons void pulsars that orbit players. After 15 sec the void pulsar releases its energy to grant creatures $@spellname1216944, increasing damage done by $1216944s1% and reducing damage taken by $1216944s3% for $1216944d sec. This effect stacks.Players that come into contact with a void pulsar empower players, granting them $1216943s1% Mastery and $1216943s2% Leech for $1216943d. This effect stacks.
